 of new york city as well as participating in numerous other charitable and civic effortscitation needed lundgren is chairman of the national minority supplier development council he is on the membership committee of the economic club of new york and is involved with the new york city principal for a day program personal lifeedit born in long beach california lundgren was one of six children after graduating college he joined federated and rose quickly to lead the upscale specialty bullocks wilshire division in los angeles at age  lundgren was married to nancy cross until their divorce he has two daughters from this marriage lundgren married tina stephan in citation needed lundgren is also the namesake of the terry j lundgren center for retailing at the university of arizona where he is also an alumnus having graduated in  with a bachelors degree in  lundgren was awarded an honorary doctorate and delivered the universitys commencement address professional historyedit federated department stores bullocks division – bullocks wilshire – president neiman marcus – evp then chairmanceo federated merchandising group  chairmanceo macys inc called federated department stores inc prior to june   – president and chief merchandising officer – president and chief operating officer – chairman president and ceo present executive  referencesedit  terry j lundgren — biography  learning the value of hard work referenceforbusinesscom retrieved    keynotes — hbs retail and luxury goods conference wwwhbsrlgconferencecom retrieved    bustillo miguel  february  retailers stop making sales forecasts the wall street journal   rosenbloom stephanie  macy’s cuts dividend and  jobs the new york times   hughes krista  september  trump says high pay for ceos is a joke and disgraceful reuters   gatti mike a long history of recognizing retails best nrfcom retrieved  april    carnegie hall medal of excellence gala honoring terry j lundgren raises  million pr newswire april   retrieved may     straus