s going to be a veterinarian i was good in science and in math and i loved animals terry j lundgren good science thought i had  job offers out of college i went to bullocks department store and had a fantastic interview but was skeptical i knew retail didnt pay much terry j lundgren job college retail im on the road two or three days a week normally terry j lundgren week road two i was the only kid out of six of us to go to college primarily because my parents could not afford it terry j lundgren parents college go related authors steve jobs warren buffett henry ford bill gates jim rohn stephen covey peter drucker les brown brainyquote desktop brainyquote mobile site home authors topics quote of the day pictures top  quotes professions birthdays social bq on facebook bq on twitter bq on pinterest bq on google bq on instagram shop brainyquote store apps iphoneipad app quote of the day feeds javascript and rss feeds wordpress plugin quote of the day email about about us contact us submit privacy terms copyright     brainyquote   loading load more quotes